Class RunOperation

java.lang.Object
esinf.model.RunOperation
public class RunOperation extends Object
The RunOperation class represents an operation being executed by a machine on an article. It stores information about the operation's name, the machine performing the operation, the article being processed, and the start and end times of the operation.
